          </a></li></ul></div></div> <div tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Tab content" class="tab-content" data-v-1d90c6ce><div id="article-tab" class="tab-pane active" data-v-02088c81><div id="toc-mobile" class="table-of-content-mobile d-sm-none" data-v-02088c81><a data-toggle="collapse" href="#toc-list-mobile" role="button" aria-expanded="false" class="toc-collapse-switch collapsed"><span class="default-heading">Article contents</span> <!----> <span class="toc-arrow-up"></span> <span class="toc-arrow-down"></span></a> <ul id="toc-list-mobile" class="list collapse"><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec0" class="list__item__link"><span class="toc-title">Abstract</span></a></li> <li class="list__item"><a href="#sec1" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>INTRODUCTION</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec2" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>DATA AND MEASURES</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec6" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>THE PARTISAN GAP IN STATE AND LOCAL ELECTIONS</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec11" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>VARIATION IN PARTISANSHIP ACROSS LOCAL OFFICES</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec12" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>VARIATION IN PARTISANSHIP ACROSS ISSUE AREAS</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec13" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>EVIDENCE FOR ISSUE VOTING ON LOCAL BALLOT MEASURES</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec14" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>DISCUSSION AND CONCLUSION</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec16" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>DATA AVAILABILTY STATEMENT</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec17" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>CONFLICT OF INTEREST</span></a></li><li class="list__item"><a href="#sec18" class="list__item__link"><!----> <span>ETHICAL STANDARDS</span></a></li> <li class="list__item"><a href="#footnotes-list" class="list__item__link"><span class="toc-title">Footnotes</span></a></li> <li class="list__item"><a href="#references-list" class="list__item__link"><span class="toc-title">References</span></a></li></ul></div> <div class="action-bar" data-v-02088c81><div class="row items"><!----> <div class="app-dropdown d-print-none" data-v-fab090b8 data-v-fb505db6 data-v-02088c81><button data-test-id="buttonSavePDFOptions" id="save-pdf-dropdown" class="app-button dropdown-menu-button app-button__text-icon app-button--secondary" data-v-f3cc3c54 data-v-fab090b8><img src="/core/page-component/img/save-pdf-icon.080470e.svg" alt="" class="app-icon icon save-pdf" data-v-d2c09870 data-v-f3cc3c54> <span class="text" data-v-f3cc3c54>Save PDF</span></button> <div aria-labelledby="save-pdf-dropdown" class="app-dropdown__menu" style="display:none;" data-v-fab090b8><div class="pdf-buttons" data-v-fab090b8 data-v-fb505db6><a href="/core/services/aop-cambridge-core/content/view/A2C4FECB10FC1DC4D8DB2BC392F13E80/S0003055425100920a.pdf/how-partisan-are-us-local-elections-evidence-from-2020-cast-vote-records.pdf" download="" role="link" class="app-link dropdown-item app-link__text-icon app-link--" data-v-63dfaf6e data-v-fb505db6><img src="/core/page-component/img/pdf-download-icon.c7fb40c.svg" alt="" class="app-icon icon pdf-download" data-v-d2c09870 data-v-63dfaf6e><span class="text" data-v-63dfaf6e>Save PDF (3 mb)
